  <bodyText><![CDATA[<h2>Whistler Early Booking Ski Offers</h2>
<p>Discover unbeatable early booking offers for thrilling ski holidays in <a data-udi="umb://document/0c45d07f55a64313a6e4bc714b58b52d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0c45d07f55a64313a6e4bc714b58b52d}" title="Whistler">Whistler</a> and enjoy savings of up to 40% for the 2024/25 ski season. *T&amp;Cs apply.</p>
<h3>Experience Whistler: North America's most famous ski resort</h3>
<p>Over 200 trails spread between two peaks (Whistler and Blackcomb Mountains) and linked by the famous Peak2Peak gondola, the resort has become the pride and joy of Canada’s Pacific North West. The resort boasts a mix of chalet-style apartments, inns, lodges, condos, and pedestrian-friendly streets.</p>
<div class="g12">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/9dff430bb4aa43bc987c0ce4f4d5b3f3" href="/{localLink:umb://document/9dff430bb4aa43bc987c0ce4f4d5b3f3}" title="Fairmont Chateau Whistler">Fairmont Chateau Whistler</a></h4>
<h4 style="color: #e02533;"><strong>Save up to 15% | Ends 31.01.25</strong></h4>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/9dff430bb4aa43bc987c0ce4f4d5b3f3" href="/{localLink:umb://document/9dff430bb4aa43bc987c0ce4f4d5b3f3}" title="Fairmont Chateau Whistler"><img src="/media/13084610/fairmont-chateau-whistler-ski-in-ski-out-2.jpg?width=314&amp;height=193" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/7070d539cae946afa9b34cb2173728fa" /></a></p>
<p>The Fairmont Chateau Whistler is one of the most prestigious hotels in Whistler, offering exceptionally high standards as the world-renowned hospitality leaders.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/482b29901f9c44c387a35de164fc1b5c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/482b29901f9c44c387a35de164fc1b5c}" title="Hilton Whistler Resort &amp; Spa">Hilton Whistler Resort &amp; Spa</a></h4>
<h4 style="color: #e02533;"><strong>Save up to 10% | Ends 31.01.25</strong></h4>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/482b29901f9c44c387a35de164fc1b5c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/482b29901f9c44c387a35de164fc1b5c}" title="Hilton Whistler Resort &amp; Spa"><img src="/media/13088473/hotel-hilton-whistler.jpg?width=314&amp;height=193" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/b0010b03c4694a89a0e9c5b0a5c937f6" /></a></p>
<p>A convenient luxury hotel offering superb value for money, the Hilton Whistler Resort &amp; Spa is a popular hotel for its great location and easy self-catering options.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/1f359444cbcd4c98abc81084d2180b62" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1f359444cbcd4c98abc81084d2180b62}" title="Blackcomb Springs Suites">Blackcomb Spring Suites</a></h4>
<h4 style="color: #e02533;"><strong>Save up to 30% | Ends 15.12.24</strong></h4>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/1f359444cbcd4c98abc81084d2180b62" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1f359444cbcd4c98abc81084d2180b62}" title="Blackcomb Springs Suites"><img src="/media/13082067/blackcomb-springs-suites-whistler-front-entrance-winter.jpg?width=314&amp;height=193" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/c019eb54039c4f4c996fc1d6f7d6272d" /></a></p>
<p>The Blackcomb Springs Suites enjoys a quiet and wooded slopeside location with ski-in, ski-out access of Blackcomb Mountain.</p>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<div class="g12">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-image">
<div class="c-card__img"><a data-udi="umb://document/29418ba1ab4e4c3a81028c3e46a803ff" href="/{localLink:umb://document/29418ba1ab4e4c3a81028c3e46a803ff}" title="Vancouver"><img style="width: 408px; height: 200px;" src="/media/13084892/snowy-vancouver-skyline.jpg" alt="Vancouver" /></a></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic">
<h2 id="italy" class="c-card__content">Discover Vancouver</h2>
<div class="c-card__content">
<p><span><span class="ui-provider a b c d e f g h i j k l m n o p q r s t u v w x y z ab ac ae af ag ah ai aj ak">Make the most out of your Canada adventure and add a few nights to Vancouver before or after your holiday to Whistler. </span>Surrounded by mountains, <a data-udi="umb://document/29418ba1ab4e4c3a81028c3e46a803ff" href="/{localLink:umb://document/29418ba1ab4e4c3a81028c3e46a803ff}" title="Vancouver">Vancouver</a> is one of the world’s most beautiful cities, and a great add-on to your <a data-udi="umb://document/0c45d07f55a64313a6e4bc714b58b52d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0c45d07f55a64313a6e4bc714b58b52d}" title="Whistler">Whistler</a> ski holiday. If you love to explore and shop, then a few days in Vancouver is a must.</span></p>
<p><span><a href="tel:01483791111" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">Call us to book today</a></span></p>
</div>
<div class="c-card__cta-list"></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/2b38e97f4ff04d62b7d3353afeee5802" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2b38e97f4ff04d62b7d3353afeee5802}" title="Crystal Lodge &amp; Suites">Crystal Lodge &amp; Suites</a></h4>
<h4 style="color: #e02533;">Save up to 25% | Ends 31.03.25</h4>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/2b38e97f4ff04d62b7d3353afeee5802" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2b38e97f4ff04d62b7d3353afeee5802}" title="Crystal Lodge &amp; Suites"><img src="/media/13087030/crystal-lodge-winter-stroll-web-res.jpg?width=314&amp;height=193" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/be2a320cc70a4956abf3f933a1d6c873" /></a></p>
<p>The modern Crystal Lodge is situated close to restaurants, shops and a two minute walk to the ski lifts for Whistler &amp; Blackcomb Mountain.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/604c5a5d57ac41d991881292b931e449" href="/{localLink:umb://document/604c5a5d57ac41d991881292b931e449}" title="Delta Whistler Village Suites">Delta Whistler Village Suites</a></h4>
<h4 style="color: #e02533;"><strong>Save up to 35% | Ends 31.01.25</strong></h4>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/604c5a5d57ac41d991881292b931e449" href="/{localLink:umb://document/604c5a5d57ac41d991881292b931e449}" title="Delta Whistler Village Suites"><img src="/media/13078012/delta-whistler-village-suites.jpg?width=314&amp;height=193" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/cb9f7d140f544a158b2e008de37f7a70" /></a></p>
<p><span>Newly renovated, the Delta Whistler Village Suites offers high quality rooms and suites combined with the services and facilities of a full service hotel.</span></p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<div class="col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-grey c-card--generic-shadow ">
<h2 style="text-align: center;">Save £300pp on Whistler ski holidays</h2>
<p style="text-align: center;">Save £300pp when you add a 6+ day lift ticket to your Whistler package holiday booking!</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/b8964cd652f24274a3e3b8c884aaf48e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b8964cd652f24274a3e3b8c884aaf48e}" title="Whistler" class="c-btn">View Whistler ski deals</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<p><img src="/media/13104122/air-canada-free-ski-carriage.jpg" alt="Air Canada Free Ski Carriage" data-udi="umb://media/0eceedb1e55e40b8bc8f0c47a927dc78" /></p>
<p>Travelling to Whistler has never been so easy. NEW to Air Canada, guests travelling internationally from London Heathrow will now be able to track their checked baggage’s journey via the Air Canada app. This new innovative feature provides real-time updates on a guest’s luggage from check-in to arrival. As an added benefit, all Air Canada bookings include free ski carriage, which is also included in the new bag tracking system.</p>
<p> </p>
<div class="row">
<div class="col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-grey c-card--generic-shadow ">
<div class="c-card_content c-section u-margin-top u-margin-bottom u-margin-left u-margin-right">
<h2 style="text-align: center;">How to book your holiday</h2>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>Simply give us a call to book your holiday. Flights, hotel and transport? We’ve got you covered. </span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="tel:01483791111" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">Call us to book today</a></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p><strong>Whistler Terms &amp; Conditions</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><em>Fairmont Chateau Whistler</em>: Travel Period March 27 - April 5 – 15% OFF. Travel Period April 6 - 30 – 5% OFF. Long Stay Offer 7+ nights get additional 10% OFF. Available on new bookings only, no group bookings.</li>
<li>Early Bird Suite Offer applicable dates: Dec 01 – Dec 19, 2024, Jan 02 – Apr 30, 2025. Not available Jan 02, 03, 04, 22, 23, 26, 27, 2025. Applicable for all Suites and Fairmont Gold Suites. Available on new bookings only, no group bookings.</li>
<li>Early Bird Single &amp; Double Upgrade Offer applicable dates: Dec 01 – Dec 19, 2024, Jan 02 – Apr 30, 2025. Not available Jan 22, 23, 26, 27, 2025. Applicable for Fairmont Rooms. Available on new bookings only, no group bookings.</li>
<li>Long Stay Offer applicable dates: Dec 01 – Dec 24, 2024, Jan 02 – Apr 30, 2025. Not available Jan 02, 03, 04, 22, 23, 26, 27, 2025 Applicable for Fairmont, Deluxe View, Deluxe Slopeside, Fairmont Gold Rooms (Does not include Suites). Available on new bookings only, no group bookings. </li>
<li><em>Crystal Lodge</em>: EBO not valid between Dec 25 2024 - Jan 1 2025 and Feb 14 - 22 2025. Available on new bookings only, no group bookings.</li>
<li><em>Hilton Whistler Resort &amp; Spa</em>: Valid on Studio, Hilton Room, Premier Studio, Signature Spa, Jr Family Combo, and Hilton Family Combo. New bookings only, no group bookings. Applicable for bookings accommodated from: December 15 – 20, 2024 – up to 40% off. December 21 – January 3, 2025 – up to 30% off. January 04 – February 13, 2025 – up to 40% off. February 23 – April 20, 2025 – up to 40% off</li>
<li><em>Delta Whistler Village Suites</em>: 35% off - March 23rd-April 30th 2025. Valid for bookings made for 7 or more nights. Valid for One and Two-bedroom suites. Book by January 31st 2024. 20 off - January 2nd-March 22nd 2025. Valid for bookings made for 7 or more nights. Valid for One and Two-bedroom suites. Book by January 31st 2024.</li>
</ul>
